    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[BrandId], [m].[CreationTime], [m].[CreatorUserId], [m].[DeleterUserId], [m].[DeletionTime], [m].[IsDeleted], [m].[LastModificationTime], [m].[LastModifierUserId], [m].[Name], [m].[TechnicalName], [m].[TenantId]
    FROM [Taller].[Model] AS [m]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [m].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [m].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2) AND [m].[IsDeleted] = @__input_IsDeleted_Value_0 AND [m].[IsDeleted] = @__input_IsDeleted_Value_1 AND [m].[BrandId] = @__input_BrandId_2
    ORDER BY [m].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_3 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_4 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[CreationTime], [b].[CreatorUserId], [b].[DeleterUserId], [b].[DeletionTime], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[Name], [b].[TenantId]

    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [b].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [b].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_5)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[BrandId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[Capacity], [t].[Chassis], [t].[Color], [t].[Combustion], [t].[Comment], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[Horometer], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[ModelId], [t].[Plate], [t].[Reference], [t].[Serial], [t].[Tab], [t].[TenantId], [t].[Type], [t].[Year], [t0].[Id], [t0].[BrandId], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[Name], [t0].[TechnicalName], [t0].[TenantId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreationTime], [t1].[CreatorUserId], [t1].[DeleterUserId], [t1].[DeletionTime], [t1].[IsDeleted], [t1].[LastModificationTime], [t1].[LastModifierUserId], [t1].[Name], [t1].[TenantId]
FROM (
    SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[BrandId], [e].[Capacity], [e].[Chassis], [e].[Color], [e].[Combustion], [e].[Comment], [e].[CreationTime], [e].[CreatorUserId], [e].[DeleterUserId], [e].[DeletionTime], [e].[Horometer], [e].[IsDeleted], [e].[LastModificationTime], [e].[LastModifierUserId], [e].[ModelId], [e].[Plate], [e].[Reference], [e].[Serial], [e].[Tab], [e].[TenantId], [e].[Type], [e].[Year]
    FROM [Taller].[Equipment] AS [e]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [e].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [e].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2) AND [e].[IsDeleted] = @__input_IsDeleted_Value_0
    ORDER BY [e].[Serial] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY

    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[BrandId], [m].[CreationTime], [m].[CreatorUserId], [m].[DeleterUserId], [m].[DeletionTime], [m].[IsDeleted], [m].[LastModificationTime], [m].[LastModifierUserId], [m].[Name], [m].[TechnicalName], [m].[TenantId]

) AS [t] ON [e].[ModelId] = [t].[Id]

    SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[CreationTime], [b].[CreatorUserId], [b].[DeleterUserId], [b].[DeletionTime], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[Name], [b].[TenantId]

    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[ModelId] = [t0].[Id]

    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_6 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [b].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_7 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [b].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_8)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[BrandId] = [t1].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Serial] DESC

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[Capacity], [t].[Chassis], [t].[Color], [t].[Combustion], [t].[Comment], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[Horometer], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[ModelId], [t].[Plate], [t].[Reference], [t].[Serial], [t].[Tab], [t].[TenantId], [t].[Type], [t].[Year], [t0].[Id], [t0].[BrandId], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[Name], [t0].[TechnicalName], [t0].[TenantId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreationTime], [t1].[CreatorUserId], [t1].[DeleterUserId], [t1].[DeletionTime], [t1].[IsDeleted], [t1].[LastModificationTime], [t1].[LastModifierUserId], [t1].[Name], [t1].[TenantId]
FROM (
    SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[BrandId], [e].[Capacity], [e].[Chassis], [e].[Color], [e].[Combustion], [e].[Comment], [e].[CreationTime], [e].[CreatorUserId], [e].[DeleterUserId], [e].[DeletionTime], [e].[Horometer], [e].[IsDeleted], [e].[LastModificationTime], [e].[LastModifierUserId], [e].[ModelId], [e].[Plate], [e].[Reference], [e].[Serial], [e].[Tab], [e].[TenantId], [e].[Type], [e].[Year]
    FROM [Taller].[Equipment] AS [e]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [e].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [e].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2) AND [e].[IsDeleted] = @__input_IsDeleted_Value_0
    ORDER BY [e].[Serial] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[BrandId], [m].[CreationTime], [m].[CreatorUserId], [m].[DeleterUserId], [m].[DeletionTime], [m].[IsDeleted], [m].[LastModificationTime], [m].[LastModifierUserId], [m].[Name], [m].[TechnicalName], [m].[TenantId]
    FROM [Taller].[Model] AS [m]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [m].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [m].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_5)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ModelId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[CreationTime], [b].[CreatorUserId], [b].[DeleterUserId], [b].[DeletionTime], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[Name], [b].[TenantId]
    FROM [Taller].[Brand] AS [b]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_6 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [b].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_7 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [b].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_8)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[BrandId] = [t1].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Serial] DESC

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[ModelId] = [t0].[Id]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[BrandId] = [t1].[Id]
